					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">- It may not be a matter of how you're generating signed/unsigned samples, but <strong>the way you're resample it and the amount of samples</strong>. In other words, <strong>AFAIK</strong>, you <em>should</em> generate the samples at same rate of the NES, or <em>1 sample per CPU cycle</em>; and do some resampling method.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

